description: Imagine a life with no more commuting in this stunning corner loft style home with sweeping views of the South End/Back Bay. This perfectly situated condo is truly in the hub of the city next to the Red line, Mass Pike and expressway. Floor to ceiling windows create the mood for this airy light filled home featuring an open living / dining area, ample kitchen with stainless steel Bosch appliances, Caesarstone countertops and large island for easy entertainment, a king sized loft style bedroom with a walk in closet, spa sized bathroom with oversized shower and dual shower heads, washer dryer and lots of storage, a cozy sleeping nook/ office. Private terrace, elevator and garage parking space #2 make this the complete and perfect home.
